Package evs.analysisunits

Store of classes for specifying Verification Units (VUs) and Aggregation Units (AUs).

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AggregationUnit An aggregation unit comprises a set of verification units for which spatial aggregation will be conducted.
AnalysisUnit A base class for analysis units, such as verification units or aggregated verification units.
Bootstrap Class to support parallel execution of bootstrap samples for verification metrics.
VerificationUnit A Verification Unit comprises the location, time and attribute for which verification will be conducted.
 

Exception Summary
BootstrapException Class for throwing exceptions that signify a bootstrap exception.
 

Package evs.analysisunits Description

Store of classes for specifying Verification Units (VUs) and Aggregation Units (AUs).
